{
  "stem": "9489.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And he bought so-- for the army, it's cheap there, you know.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Hardly you have to pay.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He got gifts.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he took me to the city hall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And who was there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The Secretary was Khrushchev.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was the Secretary from the party.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was like the boss, the mayor like, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took me to him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, he filled me out the application, mine lieutenant, you know, from the sport, from the school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He filled out application.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was shaking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't know in mine age, you know, this.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he wasn't famous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was just a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Khrushchev then was like everybody else.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I went into the office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They give me a chair.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he asked me questions.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he told me if I'm a Komsomolets, and I says to him I'm not a Komsomolets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And-- and the only thing good, I told him the truth, you know, of what's going on, why.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he recommend me to be a Komsomol-- he signed for me to be a Komsomolets.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyways, he give me the papers for my mom, the visa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they send my mom to meet a [? comrade. ?] This Polish family took him for the two weeks, my mom to their house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And what year was that?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was 1941.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'41, in spring.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] he got so appointed there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I ask him-- [? we ?] throwing up lots of food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I told him how about they give me a few pigs and turkeys, things like that if we put in fence, if we going give the food what we're throwing out to have a farm.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they give it to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We made a big farm.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they produced, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
